{"tid":545070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭民望僅38.9分　三司長中最低","createTime":"2018-01-30T07:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T08:16:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e54c32f4d3b8302e5d61d5d04209df0f50232489","tid":545070,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180130/20289729\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180130%2F20289729&d=Ttds0xcXRO%2BjCWok1iePRQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=ab83be7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180130%2F20289729&h=e5c44af9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180130/20289729</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭民望僅38.9分　三司長中最低<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180130/large/0129cwl0300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180130%2Flarge%2F0129cwl0300.jpg&h=1340549c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【中大民調】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】身陷僭建醜聞的新任律政司司長鄭若驊，首個民望評分「肥佬」。根據中文大學香港亞太研究所公佈的最新民意調查，發現本月6日履新的鄭若驊評分只為38.9分，比起其餘兩位司長為低。按照50分為合格計算，律政司司長鄭若驊的民望不合格，而前律政司司長袁國強卸任前的最後民望則為46.6分，比起鄭若驊高7.7分。<br />\n<br />\n有關民意調查在本月19至24日進行，總共訪問了731位市民。特首林鄭月娥整體評分為54.7分，較去年12月評分跌1.3分。<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗評分則為52.6分，較上月微跌0.3分，財政司司長陳茂波評分則為48分，逆勢升1.7分。3人評分均高於鄭若驊，就連同樣「肥佬」的陳茂波亦較鄭高近9.1分。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民對政府信任度跌<br />\n<br />\n至於對特區政府表現的滿意度方面，31.3%受訪市民表示滿意，較上月低3.1個百分點；表示不滿意的則有31.2%，比上月高1.7個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n至於對特區政府的信任度，34.2%受訪者表示信任，較上月低1.4個百分點，表示不信任的則有24.9%，較上月高3.1個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n■記者許偉賢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180130/large/a0203a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180130%2Flarge%2Fa0203a.gif&h=daffc787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\tDQ周庭　中央防眾志坐大<br />\n頭條 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t團結泛民成重奪議席關鍵<br />\n頭條 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t鄭若驊立會遭圍攻閃縮自爆律政司向選舉主任提法律意見<br />\n頭條 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t再為僭建致歉　被斥誠信破產<br />\n頭條 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t應付泛民質詢　態度變得客氣<br />\n頭條 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t稱盡快決定是否檢控佔中者<br />\n頭條 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t袁國強官邸運走百箱物品<br />\n頭條 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t聯署指《基本法》不容設不合理參選掣肘法律界選委炮轟DQ周庭違憲<br />\n頭條 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t【蘋果照相機】守衛香港「長坂橋」<br />\n頭條 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t眾志網頁刪「抗擊天朝中共」<br />\n頭條 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t覆核王挑戰選舉主任決定<br />\n頭條 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t挑戰陳家珮　區諾軒未獲確認<br />\n頭條 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t鄧家彪或遭方國珊搶鄉事票<br />\n頭條 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t司馬文戰謝偉銓　選情不樂觀<br />\n頭條 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t姚松炎終入閘「政治篩選　人神共憤」<br />\n頭條 7小時前"},{"pid":"72d13cc951da33e0d7aa7c08323b61048611f622","tid":545070,"uid":23445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:35:56.000Z","msg":"林鄭專登搞鄭司長一鑊<br />\n襯托自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7565b942abe829d74f385db2c7826d03f926f3ac","tid":545070,"uid":5686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:37:37.000Z","msg":"民望？哈哈"},{"pid":"a3a9b16fdf42a483db278e8a62837feb623dc5cd","tid":545070,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:40:29.000Z","msg":"可以當飯食？"},{"pid":"3c9d3ab0028f81b5b5ae6989509844b621a85f10","tid":545070,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"3成算俾多你"},{"pid":"1a6ba2c9f46321b3b2a0f9b9ab54292dc099b112","tid":545070,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abf8dd37883af859e8a720590edb5714d95216d9","tid":545070,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:44:28.000Z","msg":"38.9分 我心目中係零分 邊d撚樣畀高過38.9分"},{"pid":"298e370a59f5330a54b979b3b30b3e17657ef271","tid":545070,"uid":41198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:47:35.000Z","msg":"就算民望0分 佢都係繼續坐緊呢個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c150589678c1f137e56a1dc1bd59e8c15d9c18ee","tid":545070,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:48:51.000Z","msg":"-分都見過啦啦隊，38.9算得乜"},{"pid":"04f75e7c364b64879a12d7a276c6e9a27d565e61","tid":545070,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:49:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c81f3a80a250f24cb2545d0b0a6d10a4e6124464","tid":545070,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/30/155156_25f01fb26d7429923d0fb822ee537e51.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F30%2F155156_25f01fb26d7429923d0fb822ee537e51.gif&h=6b35403b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d35f0ed459506d6c34538b6ed2160832768c95e","tid":545070,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:54:17.000Z","msg":"有無大學教職員評分？<br />\n我覺得有分已經比多左佢"},{"pid":"ee5552c73b457b2f3c7b9352c4d2b31476556f9a","tid":545070,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d35f0ed459506d6c34538b6ed2160832768c95e","tid":545070,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:54:17.000Z","msg":"有無大學教職員評分？<br />\n我覺得有分已經比多左佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:55:01.000Z","msg":"支持警察 嚴正執法 大學生不能講粗口，司長僭建更加應該自首"},{"pid":"610bd1620819bdf572d891713c201b2649bc91b1","tid":545070,"uid":86938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:57:14.000Z","msg":"就算攞零分你依家都吹佢哋唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285969de7ec07a6d0040632c84bbaa39bd98b6ac","tid":545070,"uid"